      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "There are some leftover Weetbix in the kitchen, I tentatively help myself to two. I borrow a little bit of milk from the fridge. I haven’t smelled milk in so long that I’m unable to pick up with a sniff the fact that it is closer to yogurt. I chow some peanut butter instead. ",
            "link": null
