      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "A nap turns into listing to the Doing Good podcast by Sam Harris and am pretty inspired. Donations to charity can be thought of as equivalent (to a degree) as helping “teach” the human race; by providing positive affirmation to the solutions to ethical issues in our society. Your money earned is your vote in steering the direction of our future. ",
